entries.title_d: Saysmond Varg has evaded our nets and moved into Naboo Space.  We cannot chance an assassin of Saysmond's caliber this close to the Royal seat; destroy him by any means necessary.
entries.title: Naboo System: Finish off Saysmond Varg
entries.quest_target_d: A dangerous assassin who has evaded capture a number of times
entries.quest_location_d: Intercept the assassin as he makes his way towards an unknown target
entries.quest_escort_d: Some of Saysmond's crack pilots, only their leader is a concern
entries.failed_escape: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 Varg has escaped. The force be with his mark. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.escort_wiped_out: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 All escort craft have been destroyed.  Proceed to main objective. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.escort_remaining: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 An escorting craft has been destroyed. %DI escorts remain. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.assigned_delayed: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: <\#pcontrast1 Saysmond Varg has been located in the Naboo Sector.  New orders are to destroy him.  Repeat, destroy Saysmond Varg. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.assassinate_success: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: <\#pcontrast1 The deed is done.  Good job Captain, return to base. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrival_phase_2: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 Uploading location to you now.  We need him destroyed, no time to chance him escaping us here in Naboo space. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrival_phase_1: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 Calculating intercept course for you, stand by. \#pcontrast3 >
